      ],
      "content": "You can find additional examples on the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>OData Expression Syntax for Azure Search<ept id=\"p1\">](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/dn798921.aspx)</ept> page."
    },
    {
      "content": "Search the Index sorted descending by date.",
      "pos": [
        70035,
